@endnode
@node "distro" "Distribution and stuff"

       If you want to redistribute these so-called icons, simply do it, as long as the archive
       stays intact, and this guide, is kept abound, for the important part that is, if your
       releasing this archive as a whole. (Pheew)
       
       You can also release these Icons in your programs if you wish.
     
       You can do what you want with these Icons, as long as you keep my name in the credits.

       I have made these Icons using Personal Paint 7.1, and the "personal_icon_io.library" by

                  @{b} Elmar Plischke  ( amiga@nikocity.de )@{ub}, Bware! Great library!


       Enjoy! @{"  M a i n   " link main} 
@endnode
